00:02:50,811 --> 00:02:54,114
making a weird passion project into a commercial thing.

60
00:02:55,755 --> 00:02:58,457
So I think there's lots of talks and articles and blogs

61
00:02:58,497 --> 00:03:01,379
about how to hedge your bets during development and release

